column5: Tomorrow (tuesday) I will be heading out with my father to Rice Lake to do some Walleye fishing.  The place we usually rent our boat, out in Bewdley, is going to be closed, so the only other place I could find on the internet was in Gores Landing.  Is there good Walleye fishing there?  Most of what i hear around here is near Bewdley so any help would be great..thanks!
